Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Sooha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sudah menunggumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini indah sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lokasinya di tengah hutan,\Npasti sulit menuju ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shion bilang dia yang membangun tempat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, dia tidak sepenuhnya bohong, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, kita sudah lama menabung
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk membeli tempat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Khan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ha-Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bertemu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin semua orang akan senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal cuma undangan formalitas,\Nternyata betulan datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tidak bisa baca situasi, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang begitulah kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian pasti akan senang\Nkalau kami tidak datang,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi kami datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, ayo masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:03:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pertama kalinya aku diundang\Nke pesta ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepatnya, aku juga tidak pernah\Nmengundang teman ke ulang tahunku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku selalu menantikan\Nperayaan ulang tahun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan banyak orang seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga menyiapkan permainan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo bersenang-senang hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan berarti kami memercayai kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu yang ingin kami katakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun, Teman-Teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Selamat ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, mari bersenang-senang hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentang pesan sebelumnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih untuk itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mengirim pesan pada Sooha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dih...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang mengizinkanmu\Nmenghubungi Sooha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, apa yang kalian bicarakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak serigala?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mengirim foto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mencoba menarik perhatian Sooha\Ndengan foto yang menurutnya manis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar orang konyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat, bukankah ini manis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu benar.\NManis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kirimkan padaku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Khan bilang dia suka hewan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, ada ini dan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak suka hewan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sendiri adalah hewan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagian besar foto serigala.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena aku suka serigala.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sebenarnya aku paling suka kucing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Khan? Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh kubuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu barang-barang untuk mengusir vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belakangan ini agak kacau, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap semua orang bisa berhati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.\NKami akan menyimpannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seleramu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak mau mereka diserang vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha, kamu baik sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian juga membawa hadiah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selera kami juga bagus, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sama saja,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi bukankah lebih baik punya barang\Npengusir vampir sebanyak mungkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manik-manik perak itu mahal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, ambillah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.\NKami akan menghargainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lega punya banyak\Nbarang pengusir vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kenapa reaksimu biasa saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu harus lebih bersemangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tidak menyukainya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami menyukainya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami berniat membelinya tempo hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah hadiah kita bagus, Tahel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rupanya kamu yang memilihnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku harus memilih hadiah yang bagus.\N- Begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jangan terlalu formal.\N- Ini untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Untukku? Terima kasih.\N- Ya, kami senang
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tapi kenapa?\N- melihat wajah terkejut kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada alasan khusus, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini? Manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini anak serigala!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini foto termanis yang pernah kulihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang kamu menyukainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bersenang-senang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa.
