Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia serigala jatuh cinta\Ndengan manusia wanita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini sesuatu yang pantas kamu katakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kuperjelas di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak seperti kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang lucu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu ironis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena malam itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu jelas menjadi salah satu dari kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sementara beberapa dari kami terus\Nberjuang untuk berubah, tapi tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini saatnya bermain, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permainan Manusia Serigala.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permainan Manusia Serigala?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini permainan untuk menebak\Nsiapa yang berbohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kedengarannya seru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini cocok untuk pesta ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepatlah kalau mau bermain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Naku akan menjadi master permainan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dahulu ini desa kecil yang bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kini,\Nmanusia serigala telah menyusup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka menyerang penduduk desa\Nsetiap malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin kalian menemukan manusia\Nserigala jahat yang menipu penduduk desa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tutup mata kalian saat gelap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buka mata kalian, Manusia Serigala.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam, atau mereka akan menemukan kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pagi hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan buka mata kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa basa-basi lagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}silakan diskusikan\Nsiapa manusia serigalanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dilihat bagaimanapun,\Nitu pasti kelompok kalian, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, terlalu dini untuk menyimpulkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu\Nsiapa manusia serigalanya, Sooha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kurasa aku akan tahu kalau sudah malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu kan peramal, Sooha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, aku kesatria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu bodoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini, sebenarnya, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kesatria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kamu harus melindungiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak sabar menunggu malam tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah hampir waktunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurut kalian, siapa manusia serigalanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong tunjuk orang yang kalian curigai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu, dua, tiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalian tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana mungkin kami tidak tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, matamu terus melirik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga tergagap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kenapa kalian juga menunjukku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kamu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- kami juga akan dicurigai...\N- Dasar pengkhianat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, ayo makan kue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu bersenang-senang di pesta hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang kalian mengundangku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah sesenang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, giliran kami\Nmerayakan ulang tahunmu lain kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku akan mengadakan pesta lain kali,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu mengundangmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku belum pernah\Nmengadakan pesta ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menantikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak untuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hati-hati di jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian belum pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami masih harus bersih-bersih.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami menginap di sini malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian butuh bantuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak usah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hati-hati di jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo pulang bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa di sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf membuat kalian menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi makanan yang mereka siapkan\Nsangat enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat bersenang-senang hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku mengirim pesan lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga akan mencari\Nbanyak foto manis untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hadiah pemberian Khan ketinggalan di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku melupakan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga bisa ikut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu, tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa lain kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Matahari akan segera terbenam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:14:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh, aku malah melupakan\Nhadiah spesial dari Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus segera menemukannya\Nsebelum gelap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana aku meletakkannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya aku tetap di sini\Ndan bantu bersih-bersih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi di mana semua orang?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sana kalian rupanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong, biar kujelaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bicara padaku.\NKamu menjijikkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heli.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku akan mengejar Sooha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa gunanya mengejarnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang akan kamu katakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah terlambat untuk mengatakan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia melihat kita seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Heli...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang kita bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bisa apa lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam beberapa hari,\Nseluruh sekolah akan tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita hanya perlu kabur lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Sooha akan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Sooha akan memberi tahu semua orang?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah dia paling benci vampir\Ndi dunia ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bagaimana mungkin\Ndia membiarkan kita lolos?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita cari dia dan jelaskan dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, Heli.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gunakan telepatimu dulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia menolakku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bahkan bilang aku menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jakah, coba cari dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Energi Sooha kuat,\Njadi aku seharusnya segera menemukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekawanan vampir menuju ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang sebenarnya terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Heli sebenarnya vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan hanya Heli.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu sebabnya\Nmereka punya kekuatan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian membunuh murid sekolah kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu berani menggigit leherku juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh bukan vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Percayalah padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku percaya padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itukah sebabnya\Ndia bilang dia memercayaiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana mungkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah kehilangan Chris,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akhirnya aku menemukan teman-teman\Nyang mau memercayaiku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira kami teman\Nyang berbagi rahasia yang sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kali pertama\Naku bersenang-senang di sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi semua itu bohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heli?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia mengejarku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mendekat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paling benci vampir di dunia ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Seseorang, tolong aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong aku, Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha, kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kamu terkejut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kami tidak seperti yang kamu benci.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kujelaskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kamu vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah yang lain juga sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong katakan itu tidak benar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa aku hanya salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat pertama kita bertemu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu bilang kamu percaya aku bukan vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mengatakan itu karena kamu tahu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bukan kaummu, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, bukan begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu kenapa kamu begitu mudah memercayaiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Khan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu menangis, Sooha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu apa yang terjadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi jangan khawatir, aku di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kamu temanku yang paling penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha, mari berteman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf aku tidak bisa langsung menemuimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memikirkan kamu mungkin tidak percaya\Naku benar-benar hidup kembali
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuatku agak takut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, itu sulit dipercaya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Sooha,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin kamu memercayaiku\Napa pun yang terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga memercayaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama seperti kamu memercayaiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heli.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bersama Sooha sekarang, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jakah, apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial, apa yang sebenarnya terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa ada banyak vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heli.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:21:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasakan energi di sekitar Sooha\Nyang sekuat energinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat merindukanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak tahu\Nsudah berapa lama aku mencarimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu akan selalu menjadi tuan putriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjauhlah dari Sooha sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu yang seharusnya pergi.\NIni juga demi kebaikanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heli.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:21:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, di Episode 7,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bulan Biru: Itulah Takdir.
